Smart Copy helps you clean copy text from any website without formatting issues, hidden characters, or broken layouts.
It gives you full control over what you copy - clean text, source context, and copy history - all automatically.

No setup. No learning curve. Just better copying.

✨ Why Smart Copy?

Copying text from websites often creates problems:
 - unwanted line breaks and extra spaces;
 - hidden characters and HTML formatting;
 - blocked copy or text selection;
 - no way to recover what you copied;
 - no idea where the text came from.

Smart Copy solves all of this in the background.

🧼 Clean Copy (Always On)

Every time you copy text, Smart Copy:
 - removes unnecessary spaces and line breaks;
 - strips HTML and formatting;
 - keeps only clean, readable text.

You get exactly what you expect - ready to paste anywhere.

🔗 Copy with Source Context

Optionally add source URL and date to your copied text.
Perfect for:
 - research;
 - writing;
 - studying;
 - content creation.

Turn it on or off anytime.

📜 Clipboard History

Never lose copied text again.

Smart Copy keeps a local history of your recent copies:
 - view previously copied text;
 - see when and where it was copied;
 - copy it again with one click;
 - remove items you don’t need.

All history is stored locally in your browser.

🚫 Bypass Copy Restrictions

Some websites block text selection or copying.
Smart Copy can bypass these artificial restrictions and let you copy text normally.

🟢 Smart Status Indicator

Smart Copy shows whether it’s active on the current page:
 - green indicator — active and working;
 - red indicator — not available on this page.

If it’s inactive, Smart Copy explains why and what to do next.

🌍 Multilingual Support

Smart Copy supports multiple languages and automatically adapts to your browser language, including right-to-left languages.

🔐 Privacy First
 - No accounts;
 - No tracking;
 - No cloud storage;
 - No data collection;

All copied text and history stay on your device only.

🚀 Who is Smart Copy for?
 - writers and journalists;
 - developers and designers;
 - students and researchers;
 - anyone who copies text from the web.

If you want clean copy text, clear source context, and reliable clipboard history — Smart Copy is built for you.

✅ Key Features at a Glance:
 - Clean copy text automatically;
 - Copy with source URL and date;
 - Clipboard history;
 - Bypass copy protection;
 - Page activity indicator;
 - Multilingual interface;
 - Lightweight and fast.
